Package: CNAppR
Title: Copy Number Alterations Analysis and Integrative Exploration
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sebastia", "Franch-Exposito", role = c("aut")),
    person("CNApp", "Maintainer", email = "maintainer@example.com", role = c("cre")))
Description: A comprehensive tool to perform integrative analysis of copy number
    alterations (CNAs). It provides re-segmentation, scoring (BCS, FCS, GCS),
    genome-wide profiling, and machine learning classification.
